description:
If you're looking for a festive and cathartic way to celebrate Christmas, look no further than this Silent Night, Holy Night karaoke version!
In this festive karaoke version of Silent Night, Holy Night, you'll get to belt out the lyrics to this classic holiday tune with all the soul and heart you can muster. Whether you're a first-time karaoke singer or an experienced performer, this song is sure to bring joy to your Christmas celebrations!

Motion Graphics Used : Sis.Surangani Rosi - NAMADUMA https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKJhoXuYEfnpHXLEIuH5CIw/videos
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters Youtube Channel.
